| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4884 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 70e650e6-4eba-5c02-b1c5-3c970e8a7d82"
